---
const stats = [
  { value: "10+", label: "Années" },
  { value: "4.8", label: "Google" },
  { value: "20k", label: "Visiteurs / été" },
];
---

<section class="section li" aria-labelledby="v10-intro-title">
  <div class="container li__inner">
    <div class="li__left reveal">
      <h2 id="v10-intro-title" class="li__title">Une base nautique<br/>d'exception</h2>
      <div class="li__rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="li__text">
        Depuis plus de dix ans, le Surf Center accueille les amoureux du lac de Sainte-Croix. Un lieu où la beauté des paysages se conjugue avec la qualité du service, du matériel et de l'accueil.
      </p>
      <p class="li__text">
        Ici, chaque détail compte.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="li__right reveal reveal-d2">
      {stats.map((s) => (
        <div class="li__stat">
          <strong class="li__stat-value">{s.value}</strong>
          <span class="li__stat-label">{s.label}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .li__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--s-12);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .li__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: none;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
  }

  .li__rule { width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--c-orange); margin-bottom: var(--s-6); }

  .li__text {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--c-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 40ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
  }

  .li__right {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--s-10);
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .li__stat { text-align: center; }
  .li__stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--c-orange);
    margin-bottom: var(--s-2);
  }
  .li__stat-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .li__inner { grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: var(--s-20); }
    .li__right { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
